jsimple.json.objectmodel

Class JsonObjectOrArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsimple.json.objectmodel.JsonObjectOrArray
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsonArray, JsonObject

    public abstract class JsonObjectOrArray
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is simply used to represent, in a type safe way, either a JSON object or an array. According to the spec a JSON text, at the highest level, is allowed to be either a JSON object or array, so this class captures that.
